data.description: Single level, duet home (one common wall), 2 bedroom plus den/office and 2 full bathrooms with 1,571sf± of living space in The Villages Golf and Country Club 55+ gated community. The discerning distinction of this home are the fabulous lake views. In addition to the square footage is a wonderful enclosed outdoor living space capturing the lake views. Enjoy your meals, visit with company, or sip your morning coffee while looking over the lake. This home offers beautiful features such as vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, fireplace in the living room, crown molding, separate laundry room, Luxury Vinyl Flooring throughout, dual pane windows, and plantation shutters. Ceiling fans in the living room, den/office, and primary bedroom. In the kitchen, you will find granite countertops, newer appliances, and plenty of cabinet storage. Detached 2 car garage offers additional storage and elongated curved driveway offering plenty of additional parking for your vehicles and guests.
